I saw Tom McMillen last night and he asked about you - said he lost touch. He's tight with the Obama's and is going to be

His info is: 
and I hesitate to give him your info w/out ur permission...

Love and Happiness, Gwendolyn 
PS. Have a conference call with Jessica Joffe tomorrow.
